A teleport destination, or derived actor, is where actors are moved by the [[:Category:Teleport specials|Teleport line specials]].  This destination can be given a height (Z) value but is subject to gravity and will fall if the sector it is in is lowered or ascend if it is raised. It is recommended to use this one rather than [[Classes:TeleportDest|TeleportDest]] for [[TeleportGroup]] specials

